headline: ADM Exceeds 5M Regenerative Agriculture Acreage Goal
summary: CHICAGO, September 08, 2025--ADM (NYSE: ADM), a global leader in innovative solutions from nature, today issued its third annual report detailing its accelerating global work to support food security and strengthen the food system by advancing regenerative agriculture practices. Throughout 2024, ADM’s regenerative agriculture efforts focused on retaining participating farmers, expanding practice adoption and rolling out projects in additional geographies.
